* Verify that the the no-store cache control header is being used for any confidential pages.
> May also want to check if should be used alongside no-cache or an expires value with max-age=0 to make sure that anything that has been cached is removed.
* Review account related sections from the [[OWASP Secure Coding Practices|https://owasp.org/www-project-secure-coding-practices-quick-reference-guide/stable-en/02-checklist/05-checklist]] reference guide.
* Review account related sections from the [[OWASP WSTG|https://owasp.org/www-project-web-security-testing-guide/latest/]] (Web Security Testing Guide).